@Node "EXAMPLE_GRAPHIC"
@Toc "Main"

Example about @{b}GRAPHIC@{ub}

GRAPHIC = CPULoad, 30, 5, TRUE, 10, TRUE

(Overrides default height, pen color and autoscale modus.  Sets
 the scale_size to 10 and enables the scale bars)

or

GRAPHIC = CHIP_Free,, 5                (overrides default pen color)

Don't forget the commas if you only want to change the second or third
attribute without touching the first or second one.

@EndNode


@Node "EXAMPLE_TEXT"
@Toc "Main"

Example about @{b}TEXT@{ub}

TEXT = "Chip memory free:", CHIP_Free
TEXT = "Fast memory free:", PUBLIC_FAST_Free

@EndNode


@Node "EXAMPLE_TITLE"
@Toc "Main"

Example about @{b}TITLE@{ub}

TITLE = "VMMInformer %1.1ld.%1.1ld", VERSION, REVISION

or

ZOOMTITLE = "VM: %5ld K, Chip: %4ld K, Fast: %5ld K  %2.2ld:%2.2ld:%2.2ld", VMFreeK, CHIP_FreeK, PUBLIC_FAST_FreeK, Hours, Minutes, Seconds

VMFreeK, CHIP_FreeK, PUBLIC_FAST_FreeK, Hours, Minutes, Seconds are user defined variables.

@EndNode
